5
00:00:34,010 --> 00:00:39,890
So... how did you know?

6
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:42,580
I saw you at the bus stop.

7
00:00:42,580 --> 00:00:46,770
You were asleep and didn't get off the bus.

8
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:51,700
You need to be aware of the time and place before you doze off.

9
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:53,470
Every time I see you, you're nodding off just anywhere.

10
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:56,060
If I hadn't seen you, what do you think would have happened?

11
00:00:56,060 --> 00:00:59,810
I know. I'll never doze off again.

12
